POLITICAL: This Week
On: BBC 1 HD
Date: Thursday 12th February 2015
Time: 23:45 to 00:30

Andrew Neil presents a review of the political week with Diane Abbott, Michael 
Portillo and Miranda Green. Comedian Andy Parsons looks at the trivialisation 
of politics. Crack open the Blue Nun and prepare to watch public service 
broadcasting at its best.
